Nb6 { winning a tempo. The threat is Nxc4. Where would you move the bishop? }
13. Ba2
{ the only move to survive. Now a hypothetical c4 does not come with a tempo. Nevertheless, black is slightly better after }
13... Nfxd5 14. Nxd5 Nxd5 15. Bxd5 Qxd5
{ and black has an edge due to the bishop pair. } *

