{ was seen in Suarez Triguero,J @@StartBracket@@2084@@EndBracket@@ -Torres Ventosa,P @@StartBracket@@2334@@EndBracket@@ ½-½ Linares 2014 and black can simply proceed with }
10... O-O 11. O-O Kg7 12. f4 Bg4 13. f5 Nd4
{ and black is fine. Whitre struggles to make progress on the kingside. Idea: a6-Rb8-b5. }
