{ Once we have played this move, black should avoid arriving to Maroczy-type positions and that means stopping white to play d4 followed by Nxf3. At this point, white has three options.   Some people will try  3.Nf3  aiming to go for  --  4.d4  . Others will go for the Botvinnik System and another bunch of people will try  3.d4  straightaway. }
