{ Happened in Ashrapov,D-Dugin,A @@StartBracket@@1737@@EndBracket@@ 0-1 Pushchino 2012 and Black can release a super bomb now. }
12... d3 13. Bxd3 { and the variations that follow are very nice! } 13... Qb6+
14. Kh1 Ng4 { White cannot take since  15.hxg4?  Qh6+  16.Kg1  Bc5+  wins! }
15. Rf1 Nf2+ 16. Rxf2 Qxf2 { With a decisive advantage. } *

