15. Qxe5 { 15.Nxe5?  runs into  Rd8-+  and the e5 knight falls. } 15... Qxe5
16. Nxe5 f6 17. Nf3 Nf4 18. Bc4+ Be6
{ with equality in Tornow,M @@StartBracket@@2301@@EndBracket@@-Janisch,M @@StartBracket@@2190@@EndBracket@@ ½-½ ICCF email 2014 }
