O-O 7. h3 Nc6
{ And to be honest, white should play  8.c4  not to end up worse, but nobody wants to play that move after having played c3 couple of moves earlier.   Out of 41 games found in my database, white only went for 8.c4 in one.   Against any other move, black plays d5 and life can be wonderful sometimes! }
