{ Was seen in Ferreira,K @@StartBracket@@2102@@EndBracket@@-Calcado,A @@StartBracket@@2189@@EndBracket@@ ½-½ Sao Jose dos Pinhais 2010 and now Black plays   11.Nf3?  runs into  Nxe4-+ }
11... Nc6 12. Qd2 d5 13. exd5 exd5
{ And Black has an edge thanks to the space advantage and a bad white knight on h3. Rae8 to follow. }
