11... Be7 12. Bg2 Ng7 13. O-O Nc6 14. Nac4 h5
{ guaranteeing the f5 square for the knight. } 15. Ne4 Nf5
{ Reaching an equal and unbalanced position. Black wants to proceed with Be6 followed by O-O. }
