{ Prophylaxis against Ng4.   Now the bishop can be developed to e3 without troubles. }
5... O-O 6. Be3
{ And here we are going to suggest two paths to proceed.  6...c6  is the first suggestion from Stockfish and  6...exd4  is a line where white can fall in many tricks and the one that I have employed myself in all my games so far. }
