Nc4 16. exf7+ Kxf7 17. Bc1 Kg8
{ And Black has a very healthy position similar to some that we have seen in this series already. White's king is a bit safer but Black has a fantastic pawn center.   Ideas: Bf6, Nd6, Bd7, etc. }
