{ This is a rule of thumb. Whenever our opponent starts an attack on a flank without being castled, it is usually a good idea to strike in the center. }
12. e5
{ Probably one of the most natural moves for White, but Black is just much better after the simple }
12... Ne8
{ Because after Qb8 or Qc7 next White struggles to protect the e5-pawn. } *

