20. h5 { again we are forced to close the h-file to avoid checkmate. } 20... g5
21. Qxe3 Qxa2 22. Rdg1 f6 { Facundo must protect g5. } 23. f4 Rf7
{ The rook defends pretty well on the seventh rank. Plan: Raf8 and Kh8. } 24.
Nf3 Raf8 { The best option for White is to go for the queen trade. } 25. fxg5
{ Could be tempting but White should not forget that Black has attacking ideas as well.   Black wins after }
25... fxg5 26. Nxg5 Qa1+ 27. Kd2 Rf2+ { bye bye. } *

