{ Welcome back!   In this chapter, we analyze one of the most trendy lines in the Philidor with 4...exd4.   As you already know, 2020 has been an explosion for online chess and there have been many online super tournaments. The Magnus tour and the Champions Chess Tour have gathered the best chess players in the World competing almost every month.   In these tournaments, we have seen the World Champion Magnus Carlsen and his friend Daniil Dubov playing our beloved Philidor defense with success. In those games, 6.g3 was one of the main weapons employed by the white players.   No more talk and let's get to work! }
