18. Bc5 Qc7 19. Bd6 Qd8 20. Bxe5 Bxe5 21. Qxd8 Rxd8
{ and Black has fantastic compensation for the pawn thanks to the bishop pair and total control over the dark squares. Black is slightly better objectively speaking. }
