9... c6 10. Qd2 Nbd7 { and White has tried four moves at this crossroads. } 11.
Rae1
{ Not the most natural square for the rook, but it was employed by Fabiano Caruana back in 2008. }
11... Ne5 12. b3 h6
{ stopping Bg5 ideas. Black is ready to push pawns on the queenside. } 13. a4
Bd7
