10... Bc5 11. Nb5 Qxd2+ 12. Rxd2 Na6 { c7 needs to be protected } 13. Re1 Bf5
14. Nc3 Bb4 15. Bxa6 bxa6 16. Rd4 Bxc3 17. bxc3 f6
{ And White has a tiny edge but Black has good drawing chances given the opposite colored bishops.   Black frees the seventh rank for the rook. }
