10... Bc5 11. Rhe1 Bg4 12. f3 { a very interesting pawn sacrifice. } 12... exf3
13. gxf3 Bh3 14. Qc3
{ All White pieces are very active and there are nasty discovered threats so Black should simplify with }
14... Bxd4 15. Rxd4 Qf6
