{ kicking the bishop back and therefore freeing the d8-square for the f8-rook. }
19. Bg3 Rfd8 20. Qe3 Qxe3 21. Rxe3 Rxd2 22. Kxd2 h5
{ And White has a tiny edge according to the engines but Black is very very solid. White has the bishop pair but a worse structure. }
