12... Be6 { preparing c4. } 13. Ng5
{ if white allows c4 with  13.h3  then we should go for it!  c4  14.Bf1  h6  and Black is ready to push d5 soon, with a healthy position. }
13... Bg4 14. f3 Bc8
{ Black wants to play h6 forcing the white knight to go to h3. After a hypothetical Bxh3, the white castling would be destroyed, so White must play }
15. f4 Ng4 { The natural } 16. Nf3 { loses immediately after } 16... c4
{ and troubles along the a7-g1 diagonal! } 17. Bxc4 Qb6+ 18. Kh1 Nf2+ 19. Kg1
Nh3+ 20. Kh1 Qg1+ 21. Nxg1 Nf2# { It is always nice to show a smothered mate! }
