{ was seen in Sakaev, K @@StartBracket@@2639@@EndBracket@@ -Del Rio de Angelis, S @@StartBracket@@2472@@EndBracket@@ 1-0 Ubeda 2001 and now we deviate from the game with the novelty }
15... Kh8
{ Black's idea is of course to push the Facundo pawn and then improve the bishop to f6.   e4 ideas are in the air too! }
