23... Bd6 24. Rd1 Rd5 { This is the point! } 25. Nxd5 cxd5 26. Bxd6 Qxd6 27.
Qxb5 Bc6 28. Qc5 Qxc5+ 29. bxc5 Rb5 30. Nd4 Rxc5 31. Nxc6 Rxc6 32. Bxd5 Rxc2
{ With a draw being the most probable result. } *

